channel.title: No name shield (remodelled + redesigned)
channel.description:
ok,
I decided to completly redo this, as i found out using rs models in custom models wasnt right >.> ....
so, in this version you'll notice the skull has gone completly, and replaced with a custom cross, and custom pentacle star's, if you didnt know what pentacles are, heres a brief explanation
[I][U]A pentacle (or pantacle in Thelema)[1] is an amulet used in magical evocation, generally made of parchment, paper or metal (although it can be of other materials), on which the symbol of a spirit or energy being evoked is drawn. It is often worn around the neck, or placed within the triangle of evocation. Protective symbols may also be included (sometimes on the reverse), a common one being the five-point form of the Seal of Solomon, called a pentacle of Solomon or pentangle of Solomon.[2] Many varieties of pentacle can be found in the grimoires of Solomonic magic; they are also used in some neopagan magical traditions, such as Wicca, alongside other magical tools.[/U][/I]
and seeing as this shield is being used in my server for magical defence + magical attacks, i thought the pentactles would fit in nicely :p. Anyway heres the pics
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/35k8xfa.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/1zqalwy.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2yydr1k.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/op4tx2.png[/img]
(enlarged pentacle :p) [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/261gayg.png[/img]
Let me know what you guys think of this version :D Thanks, Gary

item.title: No name shield (remodelled + redesigned)
item.dc:creator: @the_wanderer The Wanderer
item.description:
@the_wanderer wrote:

Ok I love that design thing you got in the middle. Did you just free hand that or did you look at a picture, either way it won’t hurt my opinion on the model. I like the model, a lot better than just adding spikes and a skull ripped from RS. I’d give it a 7/10 just because I feel it is just too bland. I can’t really explain it, but I think what it is is that the little graphic thing you got on the middle makes it seem epic, but the shield base itself is just bleh. Either way I love this version.
